# LMS Platform — Backend Comprehensive Report

## 1. Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    Client["Next.js Client :3000"] -->|Proxy / CORS| Server["Express Server :5000"]
    Server --> AuthRouter["/api/auth"]
    Server --> CourseRouter["/api/courses"]
    Server --> LessonRouter["/api/courses/:courseId/lessons"]
    Server --> EnrollRouter["/api/enrollments"]

    AuthRouter --> AuthCtrl["auth.controller.js"]
    CourseRouter --> CourseCtrl["courses.controller.js"]
    LessonRouter --> LessonCtrl["lessons.controller.js"]
    EnrollRouter --> EnrollCtrl["enrollment.controller.js"]

    AuthCtrl --> Prisma["Prisma ORM"]
    CourseCtrl --> Prisma
    LessonCtrl --> Prisma
    EnrollCtrl --> Prisma
    Prisma --> PostgreSQL["PostgreSQL"]

    subgraph Middleware
        getUserInfo["getUserInfo"]
        notStudent["notStudent"]
        isEnrolled["isEnrolled"]
        oneIsPublished["oneIsPublished"]
    end
```

| Layer | Files |
|---|---|
| Entry Point | [server.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/server.js) |
| Controllers | [auth.controller.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/auth.controller.js), [courses.controller.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/courses.controller.js), [enrollment.controller.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/enrollment.controller.js), [lessons.controller.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/lessons.controller.js) |
| Routes | [auth.routes.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/routes/auth.routes.js), [courses.routes.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/routes/courses.routes.js), [enrollment.routes.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/routes/enrollment.routes.js), [lessons.routes.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/routes/lessons.routes.js) |
| Middleware | [UserData.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/middleware/UserData.js), [coursePublished.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/middleware/coursePublished.js), [enrollment.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/middleware/enrollment.js) |
| ORM / DB | [schema.prisma](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/prisma/schema.prisma), [prisma.ts](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/lib/prisma.ts) |
| Utilities | [catchError.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/catchError.js), [successufull.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/successufull.js) |

