## 2. Technology Stack

| Technology | Purpose | Version |
|---|---|---|
| Express | HTTP framework | v5.2.1 |
| Prisma | ORM (PostgreSQL adapter) | v7.5.0 |
| PostgreSQL | Relational database | via `pg` v8.20 |
| bcryptjs | Password hashing | v3.0.3 |
| jsonwebtoken | JWT authentication | v9.0.3 |
| cookie-parser | Cookie-based sessions | v1.4.7 |
| Cloudinary | Media uploads (installed, not used yet) | v2.9.0 |
| ioredis | Redis client (installed, not used yet) | v5.10.0 |
| mongoose | MongoDB client (installed, not used) | v9.3.0 |

> [!WARNING]
> `mongoose` and `ioredis` are installed but **never imported** anywhere. This bloats `node_modules` and signals unfinished planning. `cloudinary` is also installed but not integrated.

---

## 3. Database Schema (7 Models)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    User ||--o{ Course : "instructs"
    User ||--o{ Enrollment : "enrolls"
    User ||--o{ LessonProgress : "tracks"
    User ||--o{ Note : "writes"
    User ||--o{ Certificate : "earns"
    User ||--o{ Lesson : "creates"
    Course ||--o{ Lesson : "contains"
    Course ||--o{ Enrollment : "has"
    Course ||--o{ Certificate : "awards"
    Lesson ||--o{ LessonProgress : "tracked_by"
    Lesson ||--o{ Note : "has"
    Lesson ||--o{ Attachment : "has"
```

| Model | Key Fields | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| **User** | id, email, password, userName, role (STUDENT/INSTRUCTOR/ADMIN) | Roles via enum |
| **Course** | title (unique), category[], level, price, isPublished, isFeatured | Categories stored as string array |
| **Lesson** | title (unique), orderIndex, videoUrl, durationSeconds, isPublished | Unique title is restrictive |
| **Enrollment** | userId+courseId (unique), progressPercent, lastLesson | Join table |
| **LessonProgress** | userId+lessonId (unique), watchedSeconds, isCompleted | Per-lesson tracking |
| **Note** | userId, lessonId, content, videoTimestamp | Timestamped notes |
| **Attachment** | lessonId, courseId, fileUrl, fileName, fileType | Lesson resources |
| **Certificate** | userId+courseId (unique), certificateUrl, issuedAt | Completion proof |

