## 6. ❌ Disadvantages & Bugs

### 6.1 🔴 Critical Bugs

#### Bug 1: [postAttachment](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/lessons.controller.js#393-410) Never Sends a Response
```javascript
// lessons.controller.js:393-408
export const postAttachment = async (req, res) => {
  // ...
  try {
    const attachment = await prisma.attachment.create({ ... })
    // ❌ NO res.json() or success() call — client hangs forever
  } catch (error) {
    catchError(res, error);
  }
}
```

#### Bug 2: [postOrPatch](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/lessons.controller.js#196-236) Progress — Wrong Unique Constraint Syntax
```javascript
// lessons.controller.js:200-203
const progress = await prisma.lessonProgress.findUnique({
  where: {
    userId_lessonId: [id, lessonId]  // ❌ Should be an object { userId: id, lessonId }
  }
})
```

#### Bug 3: [postOrPatch](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/lessons.controller.js#196-236) — Destructuring Fallback is Broken
```javascript
// lessons.controller.js:218-219
const { watchedSeconds } = req.body || 0    // ❌ If req.body exists, `|| 0` never triggers
const { lastWatchedAt } = req.body || null  // ❌ Same issue — no actual fallback
```
Should be: `const watchedSeconds = req.body?.watchedSeconds ?? 0`

#### Bug 4: [getAllCourses](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/courses.controller.js#5-20) — [catchError(res)](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/catchError.js#1-5) Called Without Error
```javascript
// courses.controller.js:12-13
if (courses.length == 0) {
  return catchError(res);  // ❌ No error passed → message becomes undefined
}
```

#### Bug 5: [putCourse](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/courses.controller.js#96-113) — No Ownership Check
```javascript
// courses.controller.js:96-111
export const putCourse = async (req, res) => {
  const instructorId = req.user.id  // ❌ Extracted but NEVER USED for verification
  // Any instructor can update any course!
```

#### Bug 6: [deleteCourse](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/courses.controller.js#114-128) — No Ownership Check
Same issue as [putCourse](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/courses.controller.js#96-113). Any non-student user can delete any course.

#### Bug 7: [manyIsPublished](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/middleware/coursePublished.js#25-51) Middleware Calls `next()` After Sending Response
```javascript
// coursePublished.js:39-42
if (courses.length == 0) {
  res.status(404).json(...)
  next()    // ❌ Calling next() after sending response → potential crash
  return
}
```

---

### 6.2 🟡 Security Issues

| Issue | Location | Risk |
|---|---|---|
| No input validation | All controllers | Malicious/malformed data can reach DB |
| No rate limiting | [server.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/server.js) | Brute-force login attacks possible |
| Spread operator on `req.body` | [postCourse](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/courses.controller.js#78-96), [putCourse](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/courses.controller.js#96-113), [postLesson](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/lessons.controller.js#122-136), [putLesson](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/lessons.controller.js#136-155) | Mass assignment — client can set `isPublished: true`, `instructorId`, etc. |
| No password strength validation | `auth.controller.js:20` | Users can register with password "1" |
| JWT secret from [.env](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/.env) not validated | `auth.controller.js:35` | If `JWT_SECRET_KEY` is undefined, JWT signs with `undefined` |
| [logout](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/auth.controller.js#124-128) doesn't verify auth | `auth.routes.js:7` | Minor — allows unauthenticated logout calls |
| No CSRF protection | [server.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/server.js) | Cookie-based auth without CSRF tokens |
| bcrypt salt rounds = 8 | `auth.controller.js:5` | Industry standard is 10-12 |

---

### 6.3 🟠 Structural / Code Quality Issues

| Issue | Details |
|---|---|
| **Typos in filenames** | [successufull.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/successufull.js) (should be `successful.js`) |
| **Typos in function names** | [deletLesson](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/lessons.controller.js#155-174), [deletAttachment](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/lessons.controller.js#434-450), [comparePassowrd](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/auth.controller.js#10-14), [getSpeceficEnrollment](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/enrollment.controller.js#52-67), `fisrtLesson` |
| **Inconsistent response helpers** | Some controllers use [success()](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/successufull.js#1-4)/[catchError()](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/catchError.js#1-5), others use `res.json()` directly |
| **No global error handler** | Express has no `app.use((err, req, res, next) => ...)` |
| **Duplicate auth logic** | [requireAuth](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/auth.controller.js#92-105) in [auth.controller.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/auth.controller.js) and [getUserInfo](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/middleware/UserData.js#4-37) in [UserData.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/middleware/UserData.js) do essentially the same thing |
| **No TypeScript** | Server is [.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/server.js) but Prisma client is [.ts](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/lib/prisma.ts) — mixed language project |
| **Unused dependencies** | `mongoose`, `ioredis`, `cloudinary` installed but not used |
| **`main` in package.json** | Points to `index.js` but entry point is [server.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/server.js) |
| **No test framework** | `"test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\""` — zero test coverage |
| **Lesson `title` is globally unique** | Two courses can't have a lesson named "Introduction" |
| **No pagination** | `findMany()` calls return ALL records with no limit/offset |
| **No logging framework** | Only `console.log` for error logging |

---

