---

### Priority 2: Security Hardening

- **Input Validation**: Add a validation library like `zod` or `express-validator`
```javascript
import { z } from 'zod';

const registerSchema = z.object({
  email: z.string().email(),
  password: z.string().min(8),
  userName: z.string().min(2).max(50)
});

export const register = async (req, res) => {
  const result = registerSchema.safeParse(req.body);
  if (!result.success) return res.status(400).json({ errors: result.error.flatten() });
  // ... proceed with validated data
};
```

- **Rate Limiting**: Add `express-rate-limit` to auth endpoints
- **Whitelist `req.body` fields**: Never spread `req.body` directly into Prisma — pick only allowed fields
- **Increase bcrypt salt rounds** to 10 or 12
- **Validate `JWT_SECRET_KEY`** exists on startup
- **Add CSRF protection** (e.g., `csurf` or double-submit cookie pattern)

---

### Priority 3: Code Quality

- **Global Error Handler**: Add Express error-handling middleware at the end of [server.js](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/server.js)
- **Consolidate Auth Middleware**: Merge [requireAuth](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/controllers/auth.controller.js#92-105) and [getUserInfo](file:///I:/Cooding/Apps/My%20App/LMS_Platform/full/server/middleware/UserData.js#4-37) into one middleware
- **Add Pagination**: All `findMany` queries should accept `?page=1&limit=20`
- **Fix Typos**: Rename files and functions to correct spelling
- **Remove Unused Dependencies**: Uninstall `mongoose`, `ioredis` (and `cloudinary` if not planned)
- **Consistent Response Format**: Always use the response helpers or define a standard `{ success, data, error }` envelope

---

### Priority 4: Production Readiness

| Enhancement | Why |
|---|---|
| **Structured Logging** (Winston/Pino) | `console.log` doesn't work in production |
| **Helmet.js** | Adds security headers (XSS, HSTS, etc.) |
| **Health Check Endpoint** (`/api/health`) | For load balancers and monitoring |
| **Graceful Shutdown** | Close DB connections on `SIGTERM` |
| **Environment Validation** | Validate all env vars on startup with `zod` |
| **API Versioning** (`/api/v1/...`) | Future-proof the API |
| **Unit + Integration Tests** | Use Jest/Vitest + Supertest |
| **Swagger/OpenAPI Docs** | Auto-generated API documentation |

---

### Priority 5: Feature Enhancements

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| **File Upload Integration** | Wire up Cloudinary for video/thumbnail uploads |
| **Caching with Redis** | Wire up ioredis for course listing caches |
| **Search & Filtering** | Add course search, category filter, level filter |
| **Admin Dashboard API** | User management, platform analytics |
| **Email Notifications** | Welcome emails, enrollment confirmations |
| **Certificate Generation** | Auto-generate certificates on course completion |
| **Payment Integration** | Stripe/PayPal for paid courses |
| **Soft Deletes** | Add `deletedAt` instead of hard-deleting courses/lessons |

