## 8. Summary Scorecard

| Category | Score | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| **Architecture** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | Clean MVC separation, good route nesting |
| **Security** | ⭐⭐ | Good cookie auth, but no input validation, no rate limiting, mass assignment |
| **Code Quality** | ⭐⭐ | Typos, inconsistencies, no tests, mixed JS/TS |
| **Database Design** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | Well-normalized, good constraints, good enum usage |
| **Error Handling** | ⭐⭐ | Basic catches everywhere but no global handler, inconsistent format |
| **Production Readiness** | ⭐ | No logging, no health check, no tests, unused deps |
| **Feature Completeness** | ⭐⭐⭐ | CRUD for all core entities, but lacking search/pagination/uploads |

**Overall: 2.4 / 5** — Solid foundation, but needs security hardening, bug fixes, and production tooling before deployment.
